<p><b>You know you are on the right path if:</b></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You are not affected by the multitude of meaningless posts that others keep posting on Facebook.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You don't need someone else to make you happy. You find your own company most comforting and complete.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You have identified your passion and are constantly working towards achieving it.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You have made books your best friends.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You are not at all worried or concerned about what society and the people in it think of you. You are not afraid of pursuing your dreams.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You find yourself happy and content during most of the times.</p><p>If you find all of this familiar, you are on the right path, my friend. Keep going.</p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center; "><a href="https://www.quora.com/How-do-I-know-that-I-am-on-the-right-path/answer/Shambhavi-Tripathi?srid=uLaia" target="_blank">Reference Link</a></p>
